components.name: Wait for FTP File
components.description: Monitors FTP server for vendor_inventory.csv file availability before proceeding with data processing pipeline.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies, starts the pipeline

components.name: Download Vendor File
components.description: Downloads the detected vendor_inventory.csv file from FTP server to local filesystem for processing.

upstream_policy.description: Executes only when the sensor successfully detects the file

components.name: Cleanse Vendor Data
components.description: Cleanses vendor inventory data by removing null values from critical columns to ensure data quality.

upstream_policy.description: Executes only when the download task is successful

components.name: Merge with Internal Inventory
components.description: Merges processed vendor inventory data with internal inventory system to update stock levels and pricing.

upstream_policy.description: Executes only when the cleansing task is successful

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

file_path.description: Local file path for downloaded file

columns.description: Columns to focus on for data cleansing

join_column.description: Column to join on for merging

sources: FTP server at ftp://ftp.vendor.com for vendor_inventory.csv file
sinks: Internal inventory system at internal-db.example.com for updating stock levels and pricing
